1660729003492.message:
Juhyun always has been one of the bravest people among my college friends. She dares to challenge common evil and tries to turn it into something good. She never stops fighting to get something good for herself and the people around her.

I was happy when I hear that she finally found the right person in Spain. Because it sounded like she can finally get easy on her life with someone's side. That's what she deserves. And now they're going to be the best friends in their life to each other. I'm so happy that my friend who used to be a fighter now can settle down and get a bit lazy in her life.

JosÃ©, I know a little about you but as Juhyun decided you're the one for her, I too believe you're a good person like her. You have to go through many hurdles to live in Korea as an alien. But you don't need to worry about it because you have Juhyun to lean on. As she has been doing herself, she shall help you.

Congratulation to you, Juhyun and JosÃ©. 
I hope nothing but best for your married life in Korea.
1660729003492.name: Sang-uk Andersen Ahn
